  - 온라인: wish-exchange, wish-voyage, problem-solving, wish-realization, online-wish-continue
  - 여수여행: yeosu-voyage-personal, yeosu-voyage-group, yeosu-3combo-pass, wish-voyage-team, yeosu-tour-pass
- claude/SKILL.md: 전체 스킬 가이드
- claude/settings.local.json: 로컬 설정
- claude/assets, references 폴더 구조
